description: This Chainlink VRF top 9% rating Sakura purrs with a rating of 71, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 142, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 8 for North, Box for East, 1 for South, and 8 for West. Sakura has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/10712-84180-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
